The idea is to follow the chandelier exit indicator under some conditions -> momentum strategy
The chandelier exit indicator can be customised with 2 parameters - ATR length and multiplier.
Alternative: MACD (moving average convergence divergence)

Trading API
1. stream new candle sticks (OHLCV) data every minute
2. update pandas dataframe with new sticks
3. process data in dataframe
4. recalculate indicators on new dataframe
5. check if there is a new buy/sell signal (incl stoploss etc)
6. send buy/sell order (async?)


Market Data API might be part of Trading API

Backtesting.py: Before deployment of trading API, backtest
Then deploy in paper setting

How much to bet per trade: use kelly criterion

